01201250347k|script-title=ko:\u2018\ub4dc\ub9bc\ud558\uc7742\u2019 \uae40\uc218\ud604, \uccab \uce74\uba54\uc624\ub85c \ucd9c\uc5f0\u2026\uc9c0\uc5f0\uacfc \uc1a1\uc0bc\ub3d9-\uace0\ud61c\ubbf8 \uc5f0\uae30|date=25 January 2012|website=Hankyung|language=ko}}</ref> \n|-\n| 2013\u20132014\n| ''[[My Love from the Star]]'' \n| Do Min-joon\n| [[Seoul Broadcasting System|SBS]]\n|\n| <ref name=star /> \n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[The Producers (TV series)|The Producers]]''\n| Baek Seung-chan\n| [[Korean Broadcasting System|KBS]]\n|\n| <ref name=producers /> \n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Hotel del Luna]]''\n| Owner of Hotel Blue Moon\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[TVN (South Korean TV channel)|tvN]]\n| [[cameo appearance|Cameo]], episode 16\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/now/article/241/0002953071|title=[\ub2e8\ub3c5] \uae40\uc218\ud604, '\ud638\ud154\ub378\ub8e8\ub098' \ud53c\ub0a0\ub808 \uc7a5\uc2dd\u2026\uc544\uc774\uc720\uc640 \ud2b9\uae09\uc758\ub9ac|website=n.news.naver.com|language=ko|access-date=2019-08-29}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2020\n| ''[[Crash Landing on You]]''\n| Dong-gu\n| [[cameo appearance|Cameo]], episode 10\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hancinema.net/hancinema-s-news-kim-soo-hyun-reprises-secretly-and-greatly-role-for-crash-landing-on-you-137921.html|title=[HanCinema's News] Kim Soo-hyun Reprises \"Secretly and Greatly\" Role for \"Crash Landing on You\"|date=January 20, 2020|website=Hancinema}}</ref> \n|-\n|''[[It's Okay to Not Be Okay]]''\n|Moon Gang-tae\n|\n|<ref name=psy /> \n|}\n\n===Narration===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Network\n! Ref.\n|- \n| 2013\n| ''Documentary Special: Director [[Bong Joon-ho]]''\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0002601459|script-title=ko:\uae40\uc218\ud604, \ubd09\uc900\ud638 \ub2e4\ub8ec \ub2e4\ud050\ub85c \ub0b4\ub808\uc774\uc158 \uccab \ub3c4\uc804|date=22 August 2013|website=Osen|language=ko}}</ref> \n|}\n\n===H